cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SY

The paper discusses the use of deep learning in a closed loop control system for a line-following robot, which involves topics such as machine learning (cs.LG), robotics (cs.RO), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and control systems (cs.SY). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG, followed by cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.AI, and cs.SY.
